Question: Analyze water pH levels in the aquarium tank by finding the min and max readings from sensor PH-77 during the feeding cycle yesterday.
Call: { "func_call": "get_min_max", "sensor_id": "PH-77", "from": "2023-11-02T08:00:00Z", "to": "2023-11-02T10:00:00Z", "interval": "5m" }
Response: { "sensor_id": "PH-77", "readings": [], "avg": 7.4, "min": 7.1, "max": 7.8 }

Question: Export the complete methane concentration history from sensor METH-04 in the coal mine shaft for the last shift to ensure worker safety.
Call: { "func_call": "export_sensor_data", "sensor_id": "METH-04", "from": "2023-11-02T06:00:00Z", "to": "2023-11-02T14:00:00Z", "interval": "10m" }
Response: { "sensor_id": "METH-04", "readings": [{ "timestamp": "2023-11-02T10:20:00Z", "value": 0.8 }, { "timestamp": "2023-11-02T10:30:00Z", "value": 0.9 }], "avg": 0.5, "min": 0.1, "max": 1.2 }
